DESCRIPTION:<p><i>Invited is everyone 27 years or under who doesn‘t belong to the binary gender system or is questioning. If you have any questions or doubts\, please feel free to contact us! We&#x27\;re looking forward to seeing you.</i></p><p></p><p><i><br/><br/></i>Dobble\, Muffintime and more!<br/>This coming Thursday\, 14.08. you can choose your favorite game from our board game collection. Or maybe you want to try learning a new game together?<br/>If you don&#x27\;t want to play a game you may of course just come to meet people and have dinner with us.<br/><br/>See you on Thursday\, <br/>Your enBees team</p><p></p><p><i>Our youth centre is unfortunately not accessible. Should you rely on an accessible entry\, please write</i> <a href="https://diversity-muenchen.de/en/gruppen/enbees/contact/"><i>us here</i></a><i>. We might be able to find a short-term solution.</i></p>\n\n(Error: The event had no end date)
